{
  "stem": "734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Every-- every car had a guard sitting on the roof, or overlooking, so that they could see the ground around them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In case of escapes, it was, simply, shoot them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This is really what happened at that case-- at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They stopped the train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they started pulling out people from every car and count them, to-- to see whether everybody is there, whether no more-- whether more people escaped.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And this is when he-- when he took a beating from the SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And when finally we got back into the car, he-- he was so dejected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He sat, absolutely not the same man anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They really beat him badly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And Schlomo came over to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So what actually he did, I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He prided himself that he is a veteran of the First World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And he really knows-- he really knows how to behave and how to discipline yourself in order to be healthy and stay healthy and observe hygiene rules, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And no one can really tell him that it isn't so, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I mean, he really came out with it very strongly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "This is when this fellow, Schlomo, the ghetto fighter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is when Schlomo overreacted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came over to him and he gave him an argument.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, what-- what are you trying to tell me?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Blah, blah blah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he pulled out this little package in tissue paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started to unroll it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sure enough, came out a little black cross, a miniature.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is the-- this is the cross with [? clusters, ?] relief of [? clusters, ?] which I got for my heroism.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For heroism, he said, the First World War.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
